                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7444" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0745</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1597 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">跑在公路上的火车：智轨颠覆式创新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Train running on the highway: ART’s journey of disruptive innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雷辉，韩亮，罗禹歆，李欣荣，胡精英</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中车株洲电力机车研究所有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智轨；颠覆式创新；自主创新；公共交通；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ART; Disruptive innovation; Independent innovation; Public transport</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着中国城镇化进程的加快，传统公共交通系统面临着极大的挑战，城 市交通拥堵日益成为亟待解决的现实问题。如何创新城市公共交通工具，解决 城市交通拥堵的难题，支撑公共交通系统朝着绿色智能方向发展便成了一个热 门话题。本案例结合“科技强国”和“制造强国”背景，以中国交通运载装备 领域的颠覆式创新成果——智轨为研究对象，重点描述了其颠覆式创新动机、 产品技术创新与运营模式创新的过程，并对其颠覆式创新决策进行深度剖析。 案例旨在帮助学生更深刻地了解颠覆式创新的类型、特点与运行机理，培养学 员发散性思维，提升学员总结知识以及将理论与实践融会贯通的能力，使学员 深入理解并应用战略决策与颠覆式创新等理论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the acceleration of China&#39;s urbanization process, the traditional public transport system is facing great challenges, and urban traffic congestion has increasingly become a practical problem to be solved urgently.How to innovate urban public transport, solve the problem of urban traffic congestion and support the development of public transport system towards green and intelligent direction has become a hot topic.Based on the background of “Science and technology powerhouse” and “Manufacturing power”, this case introduces a kind of disruptive innovation product in the field of transportation equipment in China, the Autonomous-rail Rapid Transit（ART）. The case mainly describes the origin of its subversive innovation, the process of technological innovation and Operating Mode Innovation, and analyzes its product innovation decision-making under the new situation. This case helps students to understand the operation mechanism, related types and characteristics of disruptive innovation, and to develop students&#39; ability of divergent thinking and blending theory with practice, to enhance students&#39; ability to refine knowledge and sum up experience, so that students can deeply understand and apply strategic decision-making and disruptive innovation theory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创新动机理论；基于技术视角的颠覆式创新理论；核心竞争力理论；基于运营模式视角的颠覆式创新理论；颠覆式创新的实现路径与策略理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
